# This is a Linux/container-targeted repo: force LF line endings in the working
# tree on every platform. Without this, git on Windows (core.autocrlf=true) checks
# out shell scripts with CRLF, which breaks the container shebang at runtime
# ("/usr/bin/env: 'bash\r': No such file or directory").
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
